# MTRCommissioneeInfo

**Class**

Information read from the commissionee device during commissioning.

## Declaration

```swift
class MTRCommissioneeInfo
```

## Instance Properties

- **attributes**: Attributes that were read from the commissionee.  This will contain the following, if they are available:
- **endpointsById**: Endpoint information for all endpoints of the commissionee. Will be present only if readEndpointInformation is set to YES on MTRCommissioningParameters.
- **productIdentity**: The product identity (VID / PID) of the commissionee.
- **rootEndpoint**: Endpoint information for the root endpoint of the commissionee. Will be present only if readEndpointInformation is set to YES on MTRCommissioningParameters.
